article_id:2161,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Event, Shadow of the Mukuroshu, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/cffecc19097e250a6cef07e6924cdd37.png,message:<div>A new event, Shadow of the Mukuroshu, will start on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1620626400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>This is a limited-time event where you must defend your gate while defeating hordes of attacking enemies. You can get items used to unlock shared skills as rewards for this event, so be sure to participate!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/cffecc19097e250a6cef07e6924cdd37.png"></div><div><br></div><div>The Mukuroshu&#39;re attackin&#39; the Halidom with an army of stiffs! As they hotfoot it our way, my brother-in-law, Saiga, shows his ugly mug. He claims they&#39;re lookin&#39; for a gee-gaw from my grandpappy and asks me to hand it over. Now, it&#39;s been a dog&#39;s year since we&#39;ve seen each other, but this thing stinks like yesterday&#39;s clams. What in blazes are ya REALLY after here, Saiga?</div><div><br></div><div>â– Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1620280800,update_time1619492121